<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Beverly upped near term.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Beverly upped near term.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Merrill Lynch said on Tuesday it had raised Beverly Enterprises Inc to near-term accumulate from neutral.</p>
<p>-- Merrill kept Beverly as a long-term buy.</p>
<p>-- Wall Street desk, (212) 859-1730</p>
